{"tid":104383,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"港英時代「布政司」係咪譯錯? 應該譯「布政使」？","createTime":"2017-02-02T05:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T05:58:48.000Z","uid":29804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"889f3e703c7948d809d5187199c7a5c18e114b81","tid":104383,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"呢堆名來自 承宣布政使司，提刑按察使司<br />\n<br />\n布政司&rarr;布政使 (人)<br />\n布政司署&rarr;布政使司 (機關)<br />\n按察司&rarr;按察使(人，而家改叫法官)<br />\n律政司署&rarr;律政司(司署意思重覆，97後啱返)<br />\n<br />\n而家反啱，雖然柒啲<br />\n布政司&rarr;政務司司長(署的首長)<br />\n布政司署&rarr;政府總部<br />\n<br />\n點睇"},{"pid":"169d3370bd8893bb50fab2259acf292bcf6d6c95","tid":104383,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d222d6e64c8a4106fedbb4e201585e6fd7a47fd","tid":104383,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫布政C咪得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36866f57cf762ec3b0e6a732293e0e2a5808e3c0","tid":104383,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"司哩個講法一早有架喎"},{"pid":"3a39c03a5526f0706c277d12c920a64e6dfe3deb","tid":104383,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>司哩個講法一早有架喎</blockquote><br />\n我咪寫左<br />\n<br />\n司唔係&ldquo;機購&rdquo;咩"},{"pid":"740f7fa3e963e64fec68270afde7f358a9d0ab1d","tid":104383,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>司哩個講法一早有架喎</blockquote><br />\n我咪寫左<br />\n<br />\n司唔係&ldquo;機構&rdquo;咩</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cdcd032920fbe9a28795f9d6555bacbb5fb13b9d","tid":104383,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>司哩個講法一早有架喎</blockquote><br />\n我咪寫左<br />\n<br />\n司唔係&ldquo;機構&rdquo;咩</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n明朝時，布政使是承宣布政使司（國家一級行政區，大約等於現代的「省」）的最高行政長官，分左右。<br />\n<br />\n承宣布政使司是衙署名，其長官為布政使，全稱為承宣布政使司布政使<br />\n<br />\n清朝時，承宣布政使司常簡稱布政使司，為一省最高行政長官&mdash;&mdash;巡撫的下屬，負責省內行政事務，從二品，初時設左右布政使，至康熙三年，只設布政使一人。"},{"pid":"84402577067a6431061b25fb15f9379d4a2b1a41","tid":104383,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"本身就唔係法定語言，隨便啦"},{"pid":"63d2c4c869bd38ab07b58da0dd3bea62cdb7fc4d","tid":104383,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身就唔係法定語言，隨便啦</blockquote><br />\n研究下姐<br />\n<br />\n香港部門名，本身都亂<br />\n<br />\n司，局，處，署，會"}]}